  "3310030": {
    "name": "Realm of Fame",
    "steam_appid": 3310030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/3cc6943e3403d5e2c2da750dd16a53f8.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=405 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入一个神话与传奇摔跤碰撞的神秘世界。在这款神秘的Roguelike游戏中，你扮演Maj，一个被救赎和目标驱动的流浪灵魂。掌握擒抱、投掷和反击，在与扭曲的灵魂和神话英雄的每一次遭遇中，都仿佛是一场力量、智慧和决心的古老对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心特色:</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>行云流水的战斗系统:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握需要精准时机与策略的近身摔跤战斗，感受紧张刺激的对决。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/cf6fed5985ff3f83173a187226c30a3f.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/cf6fed5985ff3f83173a187226c30a3f.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/00006fa27915469bf9a9b69031ef964a.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/00006fa27915469bf9a9b69031ef964a.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/af4b8c7069bbefd83be8496eb8775d48.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/af4b8c7069bbefd83be8496eb8775d48.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e6b2ba50e9b0c8e94ed0307dcf608783.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e6b2ba50e9b0c8e94ed0307dcf608783.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>动态地下城:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索风暴与魔法山谷构成的千变万化的迷宫。每次深入这座被诅咒的拜占庭城堡，都会遇到曲折的道路、危险的遭遇，以及隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/ef81c897eddc58fbb13d5d0416ed07ba.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/ef81c897eddc58fbb13d5d0416ed07ba.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>传奇首领之战:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与赫拉克勒斯等传奇首领和神话角色激战，他们不仅拥有强大的体能，还掌握足以考验你技巧与适应能力的强力技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e7740ce4037681b82f34574430172c87.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e7740ce4037681b82f34574430172c87.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/f1516a9fdbaad89600bbe705b02b234c.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/f1516a9fdbaad89600bbe705b02b234c.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>神秘碎片:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索神秘传说、环境叙事，以及稀有邂逅，揭示塑造世界背后那股难以捉摸的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e10eb359367b7a1aa7e099dcc76c8da8.poster.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/e10eb359367b7a1aa7e099dcc76c8da8.webm?t=1759478491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>传说中的英雄:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maj 是一位摔跤手，因“恋风”这一神秘力量而获得了超凡的力量。然而，他的行为却意外释放了其对立面——“恶风”，这股毁灭性的力量迅速在大地上蔓延，带来混乱与灾难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/6c5c0f7c9a5852e5761cc479554dfdb1.avif?t=1759478491\" width=720 height=405 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/2e05bfb04dcffa09381a07e90456bcb9.webp?t=1759478491\" width=641 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由广受评论家和玩家好评的《The Tale of Bistun》团队打造，我们的下一个神话冒险即将来临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一次，是肌肉对抗风。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310030/extras/cdc44fdac9eabe237562ab02e8dce3ac.avif?t=1759478491\" width=1560 height=889 /></span></p>",
